<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/722206-i-have-a-14-year-old-who-is-a-veracious">I have a 14-year-old who is a veracious reader, incredible writer, and who has a very scientific mind. I am pretty sure I&#39;m going to get her this book. Is there any content that would be inappropriate for a girl her age?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_722206'><a id="like_count_community_question_722206" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/722206?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">27 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F25733983-lab-girl">like</a></span>

