        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1608697844" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18191911091602117576">Full disclosure: I knew Hope in high school, lost touch after graduation and reconnected 20+ years later (see? it&apos;s possible for good to come of Facebook!), so I&apos;m not going to even pretend to be objective.<br/><br/>But if were to pretend, I might point out that this book is about trees and science and love and sheer bloodymindedness and may or may not have made me cry.</span>
  <span id="freeText18191911091602117576" style="display:none">Full disclosure: I knew Hope in high school, lost touch after graduation and reconnected 20+ years later (see? it's possible for good to come of Facebook!), so I'm not going to even pretend to be objective.<br /><br />But if were to pretend, I might point out that this book is about trees and science and love and sheer bloodymindedness and may or may not have made me cry.</span>
